it's just the right length! At 6 inches (or 15cm or 0.5ft, if you prefer) it's the perfect companion for your Power Bank and Charging Stations. It's compact and handy, making it a breeze to slip into bags or pockets. Say goodbye to messy knots and hello to an organized, space-saving solution. Now, let's talk about compatibility. Our cable is like the life of the party, getting along with a whole host of devices. From the iPhone 14,13, 12, 11, X series, 8, 7, 6, and 5 series, to the iPad Air, iPad mini, iPod nano (7th gen), and iPod touch (5th gen), our cable is ready to connect and charge. But wait, there's more! Here are some tips to keep your cable in top shape: Stick with the original charger or a compatible PC when using our cable. It's like pairing a fine wine with the right cheese.Keep it dry and cool. Our cable prefers chill vibes over hot and humid conditions.If your cable gets damaged, especially if the jacket is torn and the wire is exposed, it's time to say goodbye. Safety first!If the connector meets dust, water, or other conductive objects, it's best to swap it out for a fresh one. It's like changing your toothbrush every few months.Keep the current under 3.4 Ampere. Our cable likes to stay within the speed limit. So, there you have it! Everything you need to know about our iSOUL cable. Happy charging!

Full Compatibility list Our iSOUL cable is like the universal key to the Apple kingdom. It's compatible with a whole host of devices. Let's roll the compatibility list: For the iPhone series, it's a match with iPhone 14, 14 Plus, 14 Pro, 14 Pro Max, 13, 13 Pro, 13 Pro Max, 13 mini, 12, 12 Pro, 12 Pro Max, 12 mini, 11, 11 Pro, 11 Pro Max, Xs Max, Xr, Xs, 10, 8, 8Plus, 7, 7plus, 6s, 6s Plus, 6, 6Plus, 5s, 5c, 5, SE (2016), and SE2 (2020). And if you're wondering about iOS compatibility, it's all good from iOS8 to iOS13. But hey, nobody's perfect. A cable that's ready to connect with most of your Apple devices.

Superior Durability We don't just make cables, we craft experiences. And we're not afraid to get our hands dirty in the process. We use our products, toss them around, play catch with them, and even take them out for dinner dates (okay, maybe not the last one). But we do everything we can to test their durability in every way imaginable, just to make sure they're ready for the real world. Our cables are like the superheroes of the charging world. They're tough, reliable, fast, and always ready for action. And the best part? They're all yours to experience.

Bend Test Our cables don't just walk into the real world, they have to earn their stripes first! And trust me, it's not a walk in the park. We put them through a boot camp of sorts, where they undergo a rigorous test of over 9000 bend cycles. That's right, 9000! It's like a super intense yoga class for our cables. But we don't stop there. We check every nook and cranny, every wire and connector, and every inch of our cables to make sure they're in tip-top shape. It's like a thorough medical check-up before a big race. We want to make sure that when our cable lands at your doorstep, it's not just good, it's perfect. So, when you use an iSOUL cable, you're not just using a product, you're using a champion that's been through the wringer and comes out shining.

Upgraded Connector Our Lightning connectors are like the Usain Bolt of the charging world. They're designed to offer maximum charging speed, so your device gets juiced up faster than you can say "iSOUL". But they're not just fast, they're also reliable. Think of them as the trusty steed that never lets you down. And the best part? They're like the popular kid in school, getting along with almost everyone. Our connectors are compatible with 99% of iPhone cases out there. So, whether your iPhone case is as slim as a supermodel or as bulky as a wrestler, our connectors are ready to fit in and get the job done. So, when you use an iSOUL cable, you're not just charging your device, you're experiencing speed, reliability, and compatibility at its best.
